 31.9"</td><td>27.5" or 29"</td></tr><tr><td>M/L</td><td>18.5"</td><td>165.=
5 - 179.0 cm <br>5'5.2" - 5'10.5"</td><td>77.0 - 84.0 cm <br>30.3" - 33.1"<=
